<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">コトバのタネ</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
      子どもが自由に言葉を記録し、保護者が見守りコメントできる学習メモアプリ
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">保護者の方へ</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        お子様の言葉の成長を見守り、温かいコメントで応援しましょう。
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <%= link_to "保護者ログイン", new_parent_session_path, class: "block w-full text-center py-2 px-4 border border-transparent rounded-md shadow-sm text-sm font-medium text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700" %>
        <%= link_to "新規登録", new_parent_registration_path, class: "block w-full text-center py-2 px-4 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50" %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">お子様へ</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        感じたことや学んだことを自由にメモに残しましょう。
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <%= link_to "子どもログイン", new_children_session_path, class: "block w-full text-center py-2 px-4 border border-transparent rounded-md shadow-sm text-sm font-medium text-white bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">アプリケーションの特徴</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-4">
      <li class="flex items-start">
        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
        </svg>
        <span class="text-gray-600">子どもが簡単にログインできる（名前と誕生日のみ）</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start">
        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
        </svg>
        <span class="text-gray-600">保護者が温かく見守り、コメントで応援</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start">
        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
        </svg>
        <span class="text-gray-600">語彙力・表現力・定義力の成長を支援</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
